law.text: Every year the board shall elect a chair, a vice chair, and a secretary-treasurer.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 163, sec. 11, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 214, sec. 23, effective January 1, 1999. -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 148, sec. 19. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 27, sec. 9. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1599e-7, 1599e-9.
